{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b09ecf12fa","title":"决定派造志愿军入朝作战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1f7e535708","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":8,"articleId":"b09ecf12fa"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"c3e6e1fa5b","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"倪志亮，当时任中国驻朝鲜民主主义人民共和国大使。满洲，这里指我国东北地区的辽宁、吉林、黑龙江三省。"},{"id":"f190e7a8ee","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"朴一禹，当时任朝鲜劳动党中央常务委员、朝鲜政府内务相。"}],"contents":[{"id":"44402fc0aa","type":"title","text":"决定派遣志愿军人朝作战","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa"},{"id":"c3e6e1fa5b","type":"paragraph","text":"倪志亮同志转金日成同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa"},{"id":"f190e7a8ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）根据目前形势我们决定派道志愿军到朝鲜境内帮助你们反对侵略者；（二）彭德怀同志为中国人民志愿军的司令员兼政治委员；（三）中国人民志愿军的后方勤务工作及其他在满测境内有关援助朝鲜的工作，由东北军区司令员兼政治委员高岗同志负责；（四）请你即派朴一禹同志到沈阳与彭德怀、高岗二同志会商与中国人民志愿军进入朝鲜境内作战有关的诸项问题。（彭、高二同志本日由北京去沈阳）","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa"},{"id":"c02d0506b0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa"},{"id":"bec3d47632","type":"paragraph","text":"十月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa"}],"page":{"id":"93e410218c","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b09ecf12fa","start":219,"end":219}}}},"__N_SSG":true}